'''Allo'''是[[Google|Google]]开发的一个[[即时通讯|即时通讯]][[移动应用程序|应用]]，其内置了一个[[智慧型個人助理|虚拟助手]][[Google_Assistant|Google Assistant]]，还提供了“智能回复”功能，允许用户不用打字即可回复消息。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/cloud/slideshows/what-makes-googles-allo-a-smarter-approach-to-messaging.html|title=What Makes Google's Allo a Smarter Approach to Messaging|last=Reisinger|first=Don|work=eWeek|publisher=QuinStreet Inc.|date=2016-09-23|accessdate=2016-09-23|language=en}}{{Dead link}}</ref>Google在2016年5月18日的[[Google_I/O|I/O大会]]首次宣布这款应用<ref name="Lunden-2016-5-18">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2016/05/18/google-allo-chat-app/|title=Google debuts Allo, an AI-based chat app using its new assistant bot, smart replies and more|first=Ingrid|last=Lunden|date=2016-08-18|work=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL Inc.|accessdate=2016-05-22|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054248/https://techcrunch.com/2016/05/18/google-allo-chat-app/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2016年9月21日将其正式推出<ref name="Gibbs-2016-9-21"/>。这款应用同时提供[[Android|Android]]和[[iOS|iOS]]版。<ref name="Gibbs-2016-9-21"/>Allo的加密功能被默认停用，被质疑可能導致被竊聽或被[[大规模监控|政府监视]]。現該項目已遭Google暫停開發，轉往新的[[富通讯解决方案|RCS]]訊息應用[[Messages_(Google)|Messages]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/122607 |title=Allo出師未捷，Google擬轉向打造RCS通訊服務 |accessdate=2018-04-24 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926090435/https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/122607 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年3月后停止工作<ref>{{cite web |title=The latest on Messages, Allo, Duo and Hangouts |url=https://www.blog.google/products/messages/latest-messages-allo-duo-and-hangouts/ |website=Google |accessdate=2018-12-06 |language=en |date=2018-12-05 |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413210055/https://www.blog.google/products/messages/latest-messages-allo-duo-and-hangouts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 软件历史 ==
Google在2016年5月18日的[[Google_I/O|开发者大会]]时宣布<ref name="Lunden-2016-5-18" />Allo将在2016年第二季度发布，<ref name="Bohn-2016-5-18">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/5/18/11699122/google-allo-messaging-app-announced-io-2016|title=Allo is a messaging app with Google built right in|first=Dieter|last=Bohn|date=2016-05-18|publisher=Vox Media|work=The Verge|accessdate=2016-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054252/https://www.theverge.com/2016/5/18/11699122/google-allo-messaging-app-announced-io-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>并随后在2016年9月21日推出了该应用。<ref name="Gibbs-2016-9-21">{{cite web|last1=Gibbs|first1=Samuel|title=Google launches WhatsApp competitor Allo – with Google Assistant|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/sep/21/google-whatsapp-allo-google-assistant|website=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-09-21|date=2016-09-21|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054254/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/sep/21/google-whatsapp-allo-google-assistant|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 产品特点 ==
Allo基于手机号码发送消息。<ref>{{cite web|last=Geuss|first=Megan|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2016/05/googles-allo-and-duo-are-2-communication-apps-based-on-your-phone-number/|title=Google’s Allo and Duo are 2 communication apps based on your phone number|website=Ars Technica|publisher=Condé Nast|accessdate=2016-05-22|date=2016-05-18|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223194317/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2016/05/googles-allo-and-duo-are-2-communication-apps-based-on-your-phone-number/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 默认模式 ===
通过Google的[[机器学习|机器学习]]技术，Allo的“智能回复”功能在收到消息后将提供几个推荐的回复选项，用户可以从中选择一个答复。该技术也支持分析图像内容。与[[Google_Inbox|Google Inbox]]中的智能回复功能类似，随着时间的推移，推荐的回复内容会根据用户的使用习惯进行调整。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Lee|first=Nicole|url=http://www.engadget.com/2016/05/19/google-smart-replies-are-dehumanizing/|title=Please don't send me Smart Replies|website=Engadget|publisher=AOL Inc.|type=Opinion piece|date=2016-05-19|access-date=2016-06-21|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054250/https://www.engadget.com/2016/05/19/google-smart-replies-are-dehumanizing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Allo支持会话型虚拟助手[[Google_Assistant|Google Assistant]]。<ref name="Gibbs-2016-9-21"/>

“高呼或耳语”<ref name="ZHPlayTranslation">{{cite web|author1=Google Inc.|authorlink1=Google|title=Google Allo|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.fireball&hl=zh|website=Google Play|accessdate=2016-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928132820/https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.fireball&hl=zh|archivedate=2016-09-28|date=2016-09-20|language=zh-hans|dead-url=no}}</ref>功能允许用户调整一个消息的字体大小，以此来表示说话的声音大小。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Beres|first=Damon|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/google-allo-whisper-shout_us_573ca974e4b0646cbeebc4c6|title=Google Debuts A New Texting App You'll Actually Want To Use|date=2016-05-18|website=The Huffington Post|publisher=AOL Inc.|access-date=2016-05-18|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190118190706/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/google-allo-whisper-shout_us_573ca974e4b0646cbeebc4c6|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Allo还允许用户在发送照片前进行涂鸦。<ref name="Gibbs-2016-9-21" />

=== 隐身模式 ===
隐身模式是一个可选模式，功能包括聊天记录自动删除、私密通知和[[端到端加密|端到端加密]]。使用[[Signal协议|Signal协议]]加密消息内容。<ref name="Greenberg-2016-05-18">{{Cite web|last=Greenberg|first=Andy|url=https://www.wired.com/2016/05/allo-duo-google-finally-encrypts-conversations-end-end/|title=With Allo and Duo, Google Finally Encrypts Conversations End-to-End|website=Wired|publisher=Condé Nast|date=2016-05-18|accessdate=2016-05-18|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202161556/https://www.wired.com/2016/05/allo-duo-google-finally-encrypts-conversations-end-end/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

启用隐身模式后，将不能使用智能回复和Google Assistant功能。<ref name="Caroline"/>若此时用户收到一个设备上没有的贴图，应用将通过加密连接从Google服务器上检索对应的贴图包。<ref name="Caroline">{{cite web|author1=Caroline|title=Chat in private with Incognito mode|url=https://support.google.com/allo/answer/6383724|website=Google Allo Help|publisher=Google|accessdate=2016-09-25|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009015723/https://support.google.com/allo/answer/6383724|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 评价 ==

=== 虚拟助手 ===
[[PC_World|PC World]]的Mark Hachman赞扬了Allo中的虚拟助手[[Google_Assistant|Google Assistant]]，称这是“[[Cortana|Cortana]]和[[Siri|Siri]]的升级版”。<ref name="Hachman-2016-9-22">{{cite web|last1=Hachman|first1=Mark|title=Hands-on: Google Assistant's Allo chatbot outdoes Cortana, Siri as your digital pal|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/3122482/android/hands-on-google-assistants-allo-chatbot-outdoes-cortana-siri-as-your-digital-pal.html|website=PC World|publisher=IDG|accessdate=2016-09-23|date=2016-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923172020/http://www.pcworld.com/article/3122482/android/hands-on-google-assistants-allo-chatbot-outdoes-cortana-siri-as-your-digital-pal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 訊息未加密 ===
继Google在I/O大会上介绍Allo后，就有安全专家和隐私倡导者批评Google默认关闭端到端加密设置的决定，他们认为这会使应用被[[大规模监控|政府监视]]。<ref name="Greenberg-2016-05-18" /><ref name="Tung-2016-05-20">{{cite web|last1=Tung|first1=Liam|title=NSA whistleblower Snowden: Google Allo without default encryption is 'dangerous'|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/nsa-whistleblower-snowden-google-allo-without-default-encryption-is-dangerous/|website=ZDNet|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2016-05-21|date=2016-05-20|language=en|archive-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521114103/http://www.zdnet.com/article/nsa-whistleblower-snowden-google-allo-without-default-encryption-is-dangerous/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[棱镜计划|棱镜计划]]告密人、前NSA职员[[爱德华·斯诺登|爱德华·斯诺登]]在Twitter上批评了这个应用，称“Google默认禁用新推出的Allo聊天应用中端到端加密设置的决定很危险，这会使应用不安全。”<ref name="Tung-2016-05-20" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Hackett|first=Robert|url=http://fortune.com/2016/05/21/google-allo-privacy-2/|title=Here's Why Privacy Savants Are Blasting Google Allo|date=2016-05-21|website=Fortune|publisher=Time Inc.|access-date=2016-05-22|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910182246/http://fortune.com/2016/05/21/google-allo-privacy-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Google产品安全团队的一位负责人Thai Duong曾在个人博客中表示他将推动增加一个让用户可以随时保持加密状态的设置，但他后来又收回了声明。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Conger|first1=Kate|title=Google engineer says he’ll push for default end-to-end encryption in Allo|url=http://techcrunch.com/2016/05/19/google-engineer-says-hell-push-for-default-end-to-end-encryption-in-allo/|website=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL Inc.|accessdate=2016-05-21|date=2016-05-20|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825160638/https://techcrunch.com/2016/05/19/google-engineer-says-hell-push-for-default-end-to-end-encryption-in-allo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Goodin|first=Dan|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2016/05/incensing-critics-google-engineer-ends-push-for-crypto-only-setting-in-allo/|title=Incensing critics, Google engineer ends push for crypto-only setting in Allo|website=Ars Technica|publisher=Condé Nast|accessdate=2016-05-21|date=2016-05-20|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709014611/https://arstechnica.com/security/2016/05/incensing-critics-google-engineer-ends-push-for-crypto-only-setting-in-allo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 消息的保留 ===
Allo刚刚宣布时，其开发者说服务器存储非匿名消息的时间非常短暂<ref name="Bohn-2016-5-18"/><ref name="Brandom-2016-9-21"/>，即消息已运抵达目的地后，便会从Google的服务器自动删除。然而在产品推出后，Google却表示他们会将会永久存储所有非匿名消息（除非用户主动删除），并称这是为了让“智能回复”功能给用户更好的体验。<ref name="Brandom-2016-9-21"/>[[The_Verge|The Verge]]的Russell Brandom评论称“这个决定将会对执法部门访问Allo消息的行为产生重大影响。现在，Allo的消息在默认情况下可以被执法部门访问，就像[[Gmail|Gmail]]和[[Google环聊|Google环聊]]的消息数据一样。”<ref name="Brandom-2016-9-21">{{cite web|last1=Brandom|first1=Russell|title=Google backs off on previously announced Allo privacy feature|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/9/21/12994362/allo-privacy-message-logs-google|website=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2016-09-21|date=2016-09-21|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106041046/https://www.theverge.com/2016/9/21/12994362/allo-privacy-message-logs-google|dead-url=no}}</ref>

